form(
  name='contact', 
  method='POST', 
  data-netlify='true'
  action="/success"
  netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
  data-netlify-recaptcha="true"
)
  h3 Hyde Park Learn to Skate, Mite and Squirt Programs
  p.hidden
    label
      Donâ€™t fill this out if you're human: 
      input(name="bot-field")
  p
    label
      | Player's Name: 
      input(type='text', name='name')
  p
    label
      | Parent's Name: 
      input(type='text', name='parentsName')
  p
    label(for="age")
      | Age:
      select(name='age[]', multiple='')
        option(value="choose") Choose
        option(value="4") 4
        option(value="5") 5
        option(value="6") 6
        option(value="7") 7
        option(value="8") 8
        option(value="9") 9
        option(value="10") 10
  p
    label(for="skating")
      | Skating Experince: 
      select(name='skating[]', multiple='')
        option(value='none') None
        option(value='oneYear') 1 Year
        option(value='twoYears') 2 Years
        option(value='threeYears') 3 Years or greater
  p
    label
      | Describe your child's skill level or skating experience: 
      textarea(name='message')
  p
    label(for="address")
      | Address: 
      input(type='text', name='Address')
  p
    label(for="city")
      | City: 
      input(type='text', name='city')
  p
    label(for="state")
      | State: 
      input(type='text', name='state')
  p
    label(for="zip")
      | Zip Code: 
      input(type='text', name='zip')
  p
    label(for="phone")
      | Phone Number: 
      input(type='text', name='phone')
  div(data-netlify-recaptcha="true")
  div(role='listitem', data-required='true')
    div(role="heading" aria-describedby="headerText")
      | Terms & Conditions
      div(id='headerText', dir='auto')
        | I am aware that participating in the ice skating class(es) involves inherent risks of physical injury, and I voluntarily assume all such risks. In consideration of Hyde Park Ice Pavilion allowing me to participate in the ice skating class(es) in connection with the institution. I agree to release and hold harmless Hyde Park Ice Pavilion and all of their duly authorized agents, servants, and employees, from any and all liability, claims or causes of action of whatever kind and nature, resulting from my participation in, or in any way connected with my participation in the ice skating class(es).
  p
    button.button(type='submit') Send